title: DotA 2 Soundtrack
description:
This is the Soundtrack for Defense of the Ancients 2.


Additionally, it contains the "Dire Shred", "Harmony of New Bloom" and "Heroes Within" Packs, as well as the Soundtracks for TI4 and TI5.

Do note that it does NOT contain the various short "Stinger" music pieces, played upon certain conditions in the game (Roshan, Victory, Defeat, Ganks, Battle Music, etc.)

It only contains the long-form (> 1 minutes) music tracks
